This package acts as virtual Kinect with an .oni file.

Installation
 1. roscd openni_ros/
 2. rosdep install openni_camera_deprecated

Usage
 1. roscore
    if 'roscore' is already running skip this step.
 2. roslaunch openni_camera_deprecated openni_node.launch file_path:=/examplefolder/example.oni to_be_repeated:=false
    please change '/examplefolder/example.oni' with the correct path of intented oni file.
    please change 'to_be_repeated:=false' with 'to_be_repeated:=true' if you want the stream be repeated.
